citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process between 1:30-2:00pm
on 23-OCT-2023. A worker on the property stated the licensees had gone to town on some errands and wasn't sure when
they would be back. There was no answer to a phone call and voicemail box was full.
End Section

Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.

they would be back. There was no answer to a phone call and voicemail box was full.
